Bar Manager

o¿reilly¿s was established in March 1994. We are an Irish family owned and operated pub group. We pride ourselves in our hospitality, delicious homemade food & a fine pint, which is served up in a friendly, relaxed atmosphere, making o¿reilly¿s a true home from home.

Are you looking for an exciting, new experience? Have you built a career in the bar industry and are now ready to manage a bar of a successful international Irish pub chain? We operate 7 venues throughout Europe and are looking for someone to manage one of our pubs located in Germany.


The role encompasses the following key tasks:

Hiring, training, assessing and developing a high quality team;
Increasing company revenue through the implementation of new marketing ideas;
Maintaining the costs outlined by the budget;
Creating monthly rosters, ensuring staff are budgeted their contracted hours;
Leading and motivating a young, international team.


The following skills are required:

Good computer skills, including a good knowledge of the MS Office package;
A high attention to detail;
Advanced organizational and planning skills;
Exceptional leadership skills;
Good people skills.


The following skills are desired:

German language skills;
